    "demonstrated the potential of VR simulators in real-time skill assessment, where motion data from novice to expert trainees was analyzed using machine learning to categorize skill levels based on recorded actions [113].",
    "Such VR-based assessments, when paired with data-driven feedback, enable training programs to evaluate skill progression.",
    "Gazit et al.",
    "developed a virtual reality laparoscopic simulator to assess technical aptitude for selecting surgical residents [114].",
